title: Catalan Crisis: Thousands rally against Catalan independence
description:
Hundreds of thousands of pro-unity Catalans have rallied in the streets of Barcelona. It was a strong show of support for a united Spain, following the region's declaration of independence. But as Sarah Morice reports, it's also a clear indication of how divided the region has become.
